item.title: Love Is A Bird...
item.description:
Love Is A Bird...

I just absolutely loved this pic from Adriana & Jeff's engagement photo, I wanted to share it separately! The quote that goes with it makes me smile. It's these photos that tell a story and capture the connection between a couple that makes me do what I do! "Love is a bird.

item.title: Dubi & Chase's Wedding, Spencer's on the Waterfront Burlington
item.description:
Dubi & Chase's Wedding, Spencer's on the Waterfront Burlington

Where to even start with Dubi & Chase's wedding! From the epic wedding location (Spencer's on the Waterfront in Burlington) to the amazing backdrops at the Art Gallery of Burlington - I loved spending the day with these two. Dubi is a riot - and my stomach hurt at the end of the day from...
